<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.8.6">
<l>cūḻkaṇ ṭāyeṉ ṟollai viṉaiyai yaṟuttu ṉaṭicēru</l>
<l>mūḻkaṇ ṭiruntē tūrāk kuḻitūrt teṉainā ḷakaṉṟiruppaṉ</l>
<l>vāḻtol pukaḻār kuṭantaik kiṭantāy vāṉōr kōmāṉē</l>
<l>yāḻi ṉicaiyē yamutē yaṟiviṉ payaṉē yariyēṟē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Think, see, cutting off my ancient karma. Keeping seeing the occasion</l>
<l>to join your feet, how many days will I be separated [from you], filling up a pit that does not fill,</l>
<l>o you who lie in Kuṭantai of those with living ancient fame, king of the celestials,</l>
<l>music of the lute, ambrosia, fruit of knowledge, bull among lions?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
